{"word":"G3893 - παραπικραίνω - parapikraínō - par-ap-ik-rah'-ee-no - Provoke","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">παραπικραίνω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">parapikraínō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">par-ap-ik-rah'-ee-no</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Provoke</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - கோபமூட்டு"},{"paragraph":"to provoke, to exasperate; to rouse to indignation"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G3844 - παρά - pará - par-ah'/3844\">G3844</a> and <a href=\"#/G4087 - πικραίνω - pikraínō - pik-rah'-ee-no/4087\">G4087</a>; to <i>embitter alongside</i>, that is, (figuratively) to <i>exasperate:</i> - provoke.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G3893/3893\">G3893</a>, <a href=\"#/G3894/3894\">G3894</a>, <a href=\"#/G4087/4087\">G4087</a>, <a href=\"#/G4088/4088\">G4088</a>, <a href=\"#/G4089/4089\">G4089</a>, <a href=\"#/G4090/4090\">G4090</a>"}]}